    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "\ud83d\udd27 Budget-Friendly Fixer or Parts Car \u2014 Priced to Move! \ud83d\udd27\n\nLooking for a project or a super-affordable option? Here's your chance! We'll be completely honest: this vehicle is in poor condition and shows its age \u2014 expect significant wear, mechanical issues, and cosmetic imperfections that will need attention. It's not a daily driver in its current state, but for the right buyer \u2014 a DIY mechanic, someone looking for parts, or a dedicated hobbyist \u2014 there's real opportunity here. Priced accordingly so you know exactly what you're getting: no surprises, just a straight deal!",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
